@glen could you please check this out?

Hello,


We'd like to update our workplace giving page: https://msra.org.au/ways-to-donate/workplace-giving/


Please find attached a word document with the copy changes required. We'd like to set up the page similar to this page https://msra.org.au/ways-to-donate/gifts-in-wills/ if possible so the content is more dynamic then what we have now. This will include embedding a form on the page also as well as icons (attached) - see word doc for details of form.


I have also attached the pdfs that we'd like added in when clicking on the relevant Workplace Giving downloadable resources section. I have attached the icons/infographics that we have specified in the word doc as well as the pdfs of the resources.


Should you need any further imagery for this page - please let me know.


Look forward to seeing what we can do with this page - if there are any questions, happy to answer.


Kind regards,
Jess
